WEBVTT

00:02:58.520 --> 00:03:02.320
and I had a piece of gray hair.

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:05.440
Alright --

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:08.040
please take off your blindfolds.

00:03:10.760 --> 00:03:13.040
Welcome to the performance world.

00:03:13.520 --> 00:03:16.880
First of all, let's explain
what the performance is.

00:03:17.840 --> 00:03:20.376
So many artists,
so many different explanations,

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:23.160
but my explanation
for performance is very simple.

00:03:23.640 --> 00:03:28.216
Performance is a mental
and physical construction

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:31.056
that the performer makes
in a specific time